release_note: Hey-hey! While we're working on the new version, it's time to fix some old bugs.
WIDGETS Now you can keep all information about your actions at a glance with widgets (available only for iOS 14)

HABITS They say you only need 21 days to turn an action into a habit. The only way to find out if it's true is to try. Add at least one activity a day for 21 days, and unlock all sassy comments from a built-in Haptic AI.
You asked. We listened. Now you can hide default categories in settings. And, actually, any unwanted category, yay!
